local BlockPlayer = require "actions/BlockPlayer" local NumScreen = require "actions/NumScreen" local Serial = require "actions/Serial" local Ease = require "actions/Ease" local Wait = require "actions/Wait" local Do = require "actions/Do" local Action = require "actions/Action" local PlayAudio = require "actions/PlayAudio"
return function(self) local wallLayer for _,layer in pairs(self.scene.map.layers) do if layer.name == "RightWall" then wallLayer = layer break end end
local onSuccess = Action() if not GameState:isFlagSet(self.scene.objectLookup.RightEntranceBlock) then onSuccess = Serial { Ease(self.scene.camPos, "x", -200, 1), PlayAudio("sfx", "openchasm", 1.0, true), Ease(wallLayer, "offsety", -32*3, 1), Ease(self.scene.camPos, "x", 0, 1), Do(function() self.scene.objectLookup.RightEntrance.y = self.scene.objectLookup.RightEntranceBlock.y self.scene.objectLookup.RightEntrance.object.y = self.scene.objectLookup.RightEntranceBlock.y self.scene.objectLookup.RightEntrance:updateCollision() self.scene.objectLookup.RightEntranceBlock:remove() GameState:setFlag(self.scene.objectLookup.RightEntranceBlock) end) } end self.scene.player.cinematicStack = self.scene.player.cinematicStack + 1 return BlockPlayer { Wait(0.8), NumScreen {prompt="Enter access code", expected="1683", success=onSuccess}, Do(function() self.scene.player.cinematicStack = self.scene.player.cinematicStack - 1 end) } end
